  "titleEn": "Interrogative Particles",
  "description": "Learn question words: أَيْنَ (where), كَيْفَ (how), مَتَى (when), لِمَاذَا (why), كَمْ (how many).",
  "vocabulary": ["word-184", "word-186", "word-185", "word-187", "word-188", "word-227"],
  "grammarPoints": ["gp-031", "gp-032"],
  "notes": [
    {
      "title": "Question Words (أدوات الاستفهام)",
      "titleArabic": "أدوات الاستفهام",
      "content": [
        "Arabic has several interrogative words used to ask questions. These particles are placed at the beginning of the sentence.",
        "Some interrogative words are particles (حروف) while others are nouns (أسماء). This affects the grammar of the sentence."
      ],
      "keyPoints": [
        "أَيْنَ - where (indicates place)",
        "كَيْفَ - how (indicates manner/state)",
        "مَتَى - when (indicates time)",
        "لِمَاذَا / لِمَ - why (indicates reason)",
        "كَمْ - how many/much (indicates quantity)"
      ],
      "examples": [
        { "arabic": "أَيْنَ الْكِتَابُ؟", "english": "Where is the book?" },
        { "arabic": "كَيْفَ حَالُكَ؟", "english": "How are you?" },
        { "arabic": "مَتَى تَذْهَبُ؟", "english": "When do you go?" },
        { "arabic": "لِمَاذَا ذَهَبْتَ؟", "english": "Why did you go?" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Using كَمْ and أَيُّ",
      "titleArabic": "استخدام كم وأيّ",
      "content": [
        "كَمْ (how many/much) is followed by a noun in the accusative singular (تمييز) when asking about quantity.",
        "أَيُّ (which) agrees with its noun in gender and is used for selection among options."
      ],
      "keyPoints": [
        "كَمْ كِتَابًا؟ - How many books? (accusative singular)",
        "أَيُّ كِتَابٍ؟ - Which book? (genitive after أَيّ)",
        "أَيَّةُ سَاعَةٍ؟ - Which hour? (feminine form)",
        "كَمْ can also mean 'how much' with uncountable nouns"
      ],
      "examples": [
        { "arabic": "كَمْ طَالِبًا فِي الْفَصْلِ؟", "english": "How many students are in the class?" },
        { "arabic": "أَيُّ كِتَابٍ تُرِيدُ؟", "english": "Which book do you want?" },
        { "arabic": "كَمِ السَّاعَةُ؟", "english": "What time is it?" },
        { "arabic": "أَيُّهُمْ أَفْضَلُ؟", "english": "Which of them is better?" }
      ]
    }
  ],
